# Enhanced .gitignore for RepoKit Projects
# This template provides comprehensive exclusions for various languages and tools

#######################
# Common ignored files #
#######################
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.log
*.tmp
*.bak
*.swp
*~

